<li id="cite_note-81"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-81">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text">René Pomeau, <i>Voltaire en son temps</i>, tome 5, <abbr class="abbr" title="page">p.</abbr>&#160;319.</span>
